# Agent Refresh Pack Template

::summary
Use this template for documents that an agent should revisit on a fixed cadence without rewriting unrelated source.
::

::instruction{id="refresh-instructions" scope="agent"}
Discover IDs first, patch only targeted blocks, preserve aliases, run validation after edits, and summarize changed blocks in the final response.
::

::claim{id="tracked-claim" confidence=0.68}
Write the claim that should be checked repeatedly.
::

::evidence{id="tracked-evidence" for="tracked-claim" source="tracked-source"}
Write the evidence that should be refreshed when the source changes.
::

::citation{id="tracked-source" accessed="2026-05-14" href="https://example.com/tracked"}
Tracked source placeholder.
::

::agent_task{id="weekly-refresh" scope="weekly"}
Check whether `tracked-source` changed, update `tracked-evidence` if needed, and leave all unrelated blocks unchanged.
::
